title: Grateful Dead Live at Nassau Coliseum on 1992-03-12
description:
Set 1

Greatest Story Ever Told, Bertha, Walkin' Blues, Stagger Lee, Beat It On Down The Line, Just Like Tom Thumb's Blues, Tennessee Jed, Promised Land

Set 2

Saint Of Circumstance, Ship of Fools, Corinna, Playin' In The Band Reprise-> Drums-> Jam-> The Other One-> Stella Blue-> Sugar Magnolia, E: It's All Over Now Baby Blue
